text: Shebbeare is a surname, and may refer to: *John Shebbeare (1709–1788), British Tory political satirist *Robert Shebbeare (1827–1860), English recipient of the Victoria Cross *Edward Oswald Shebbeare (1884-1964), British mountaineer, naturalist and forester *Tom Shebbeare (born 1952), British business executive
